<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Megan Fox and her beau Machine Gun Kelly were spotted arriving to the Mayan Theater in Downtown Los Angeles on Thursday evening.</p>

<p>The 34-year-old actress showed support for the 30-year-old rapper as he appeared to celebrate the release of his album Tickets To My Downfall at the historic venue.</p>

<p>Fox cut a casual figure in a vintage band tee and a pair of black skinny jeans with an edgy raw hem as Machine Gun Kelly walked with his arm wrapped around her.</p>

