<p>For the celebratory evening, he donned a blue polo-style sweater that featured a circle pattern throughout and a button-up front.</p>

<p>Kelly paired the unique top with a pair of white trousers and some coordinating sneakers.</p>

<p>His signature bleach blonde hair looked noticeably undone and he had what looked to be a string of pearls around his neck. </p>

